```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Simple Web App</title>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Welcome to Our Web App</h1>
